STRENGTH

Usage       : cast 'strength' <victim>

When cast, the victim will feel an increase in his strength.
#
SUMMON

Usage       : cast 'summon' <victim>

Will summon a person of the name spoken.
#
"WORD OF RECALL"

Usage       : cast 'word of recall' 

The caster will be transferred back to the last place in which they rented
at.
